oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mary A. Carter
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Copy print of an oval portrait of Mary A. "Marianne" Carter.

Mary A. "Marianne" Carter was born in Arlington/Kerrville, Tennessee. She was married to Samuel Burns (1749-July 18, 1922) and they are both buried in the Ludicia Cemetery in Arlington, Tennessee. She was the daughter of Henry Carter Sr. and Sophie Chester Carter. She is the great-great-great aunt of the donor.
